data.description:
Available December 1st. 
*A private bedroom available for $700 with shared common space. 
*A beautiful 2-story freshly painted condominium in Cedar Park at the Paradiso Villas Community!
*Across the street is Brushy Creek Lake Park that has hike & bike trails, fishing, kayaking, etc. Other amenities close by are public golf course, jogging/biking path, lake privileges, park, and sport court. Free access to beautiful community swimming pool!
*Very easy access to Hwy 183, 45 & I30 Toll road.
*Conveniently located near shopping, dining, restaurants, movie theaters, and the new Round Rock donuts location!
*Enter into vaulted ceilings and an open concept floor-plan with living room, kitchen, and dining area. A lovely kitchen with a 4-burner gas stove, granite counters, and spacious pantry. Cute powder room near kitchen door entrance. Cozy porch area. And a 2 car garage! Bright kitchen with breakfast bar overlooking the dining area and spacious living room. Master suite downstairs with full bath, walk-in shower and walk-in closet. Remaining bedrooms and full bath upstairs, along with a laundry room, and media room to relax during that downtime!
*Excellent Cedar Park location with highly top rated schools throughout the district: Reagan Elementary School, Cypress Elementary School, Harmony Science Academy, Henry Middle School, Cedar Park High School, Vista Ridge High School.
 
Looking forward to hearing from you soon!

RENTAL TERMS: will be executed through a contract
*700 per month with 1 month's security deposit due at signing of lease.
 Lease terms: 12-24 months
 Credit score: 600+
 Background check for all occupants 18yrs & above
 Pets welcome - nonrefundable fee of $350
 No smoking
 Tenants to pay for all utilities (Electricity, gas, water, internet, cable)
